TradingView Alerts Manager - Backup, Restore, Migrate, Delete

Easily manage your TradingView alerts with this extension. Backup your alerts to a JSON/CSV file, restore or migrate them across devices, or delete all alerts with a single click. Simplify your alert management and keep your trading strategies organized and secure.
